pr_body: This pull has the entirety of the coding work done during GSoC '20. This included the entry of the rough model as well as the linkage of the model to BioGears systemic circulation, followed by adjustment of the time variable to account for different administration times and the entry of literature-based rate constants where possible in the model. Two rate constants were adjusted for after validation data was incorporated, allowing for a much better fit of literature data. Additional V&V is required for a merge, but the pull request is here to indicate completion of the GSoC period.
